title: Winnipeg Jets VS Kings Last Regular Season Game Disc 1 and 2 Unc
description:
This is the Winnipeg Jets VS L.A Kings live at the Winnipeg Arena on April 12th/1996. It was the last ever regular season game for the historic Franchise before the move to the "hot-bed" of hockey, Phoenix the following season. 

Keith Tkachuk notches his 50th goal with under a second left to clinch the win and more importantly; the first playoff appearance since 1993. Sit back, and enjoy one of the greatest Winnipeg Jets games & the NHL&#039;s greatest fans! 

Bring&#039;em Back
